{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究物体的运动与阻力之间的关系。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">运动的物体之所以会停下来是因为受到了阻力。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小车（</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个）、带斜面的木板（</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块，其中两块分别铺有毛巾、棉布）</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拖动小车放置在斜面上，分别让小车从三个斜面的同一高度由静止开始滑下，直至小车停止运动；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过斜面上的刻度测出小车停止运动时在水平面上滑行的距离。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平面越光滑，小车运动的距离越长，说明小车受到的阻力越小，速度减小的越慢。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如果小车运动时不受阻力，它会一直运动下去，不会停下来。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}